FirstRand Won’t Appeal Zambia Move on Bank, Business Day Says

-- B y   A n d r e s   R .   M a r t i n e z
-- 
2011-10-10T05:42:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/firstrand-won-t-appeal-zambia-move-on-bank-business-day-says.html
FirstRand Ltd. won’t fight the
decision by the Zambian government to cancel the purchase of
Finance Bank Zambia Ltd., Business Day reported, citing Michael Jordaan, chief executive officer of FirstRand’s  First National
Bank .  FirstRand is working with the government to unwind the deal
and remove staff from the country, the Johannesburg-based
newspaper cited Jordaan as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andres R. Martinez in johannesburg at 
 amartinez28@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  